Package hu.bme.mit.theta.core.dsl.gen

Class CoreDslBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.core.dsl.gen.CoreDslBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
CoreDslListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class CoreDslBaseListener extends Object implements CoreDslListener
This class provides an empty implementation of CoreDslListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
